TITLEDesignated SurvivorSTARRINGKiefer Sutherland, Natascha McElhone, Adan Canto GENREDrama, ThrillerRelease DateSeptember 21 When the Cabinet convenes at the Capital building, one member is kept at a secret location; he is known as the designated survivor. When Secretary Tom Kirkman is asked to be the designated survivor, his life changes overnight after the Capital is blown up and every member of the Cabinet including the President are declared dead. Kirkman, a politician of little experience, is immediately sworn in as the new President. Unaware that the attack on the Capital was just the beginning, Kirkman struggles to fit in his new role as the leader of the free world. Designated Survivor delivers on its political intrigue and is compelling in its suspense. Star Rating: 4/5